  "siteName": "卡尔的AI沃茨",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=767864ed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXk00diavJYADGFClnPAZrGPll1uRMRImGQh99IZJU81TiaZ26RXuh5O81pCFCafVVb3icxpsRkAKr5kw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:#8f959e;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:#8f959e;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年吃了太多麦当当了，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我决定做一个广告纪念一下麦当劳在国内开业的35周年，实话说，我没想过年底我就能</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">两段提示语</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">做出一段这样的产品广告，</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个效果立马点燃我的兴奋点了，我一个翻身起床又是熬了几个夜玩了超多种类型的广告，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如还是这个麦乐鸡，我甚至没有改原本提示语的内容，只是又run了一遍这个工作流，就又得到了一个这样的视频。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且它的效果都是和我工作流中间步骤生成的九宫格分镜图，都能一一对应上！</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019504\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5462962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f156569&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXk00diavJYADGFClnPAZrGPliaPm4IcXREP2v2icFIwN4sbEkc5IVcaqM5rIRowa33JrM6S5iaZic39pSg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(216, 57, 49) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">重要的是，我没有分开生图生视频！没有动手剪辑！没有手动配音配乐！</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">全程就只有两段提示语，然后点击一下Run，就可以了！好好好，AI广告已经能这么玩了是吧？以前总觉得AI一键成片还是有那么一段距离的，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">至少之前我一句话做出来的成片上，人物场景的一致性，剧情的完整度以及转场运镜的设计都是差了那么一点意思。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">但现在，此时此刻，right now</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我就只用这两个提示语玩出了N多不同的广告片，中间只替换了初始提供的产品素材，我就做出了</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">动画版麦乐鸡宣传片，</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">3D动画版麦当当汉堡宣传片，</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至我还给海底捞火锅杯做了一个广告，</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">你要说这工作流做出来的视频，一个两个是偶然成功，那五条片子一次过够稳定了吧，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我从未感觉自己成片率如此高过。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">如此好用之工作流，必须让大家都用上。这次我用的是Open</span><span leaf=\"\">C</span><span leaf=\"\">reator，也直接发布了我的工作流，既能生成真人实拍风格TVC、动画风格TVC、还能做自己的动漫小短片等等，都在这一个画布上了，感兴趣的大家可以直接去用。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019507\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5885416666666666\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/YEhakvKZjXk00diavJYADGFClnPAZrGPlV0Pgx7ic9C1ewK4gwiceUkQ4XVWLgnsvZvuuVAZGeYUkibiaaxJD2We2RA/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"340\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a42184d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FYEhakvKZjXk00diavJYADGFClnPAZrGPlV0Pgx7ic9C1ewK4gwiceUkQ4XVWLgnsvZvuuVAZGeYUkibiaaxJD2We2RA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://opencreator.io/canvas?shareid=693ab2d72663\" target=\"_blank\">https://opencreator.io/canvas?shareid=693ab2d72663</a></span></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单讲解一下这个工作流吧，其实非常简单，主要的逻辑就是上传一个产品图后拉一个图生图节点，使用BananaPro图生图做出一张九宫格分镜图，提示语用这个就行，中间关于剧情和主人公的描述可以自行替换，</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"background-color:rgb(103, 84, 140);border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:8px;padding:4px 14px;place-items:flex-start;display:flex;margin-top:16px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left !important;\">\n      <span style=\"align-items: center;justify-content: center;display: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">💡</span></span></span>\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n       <p style=\"margin:8px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;width:100%;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">你是一个专业的</span></span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;background-color:rgb(103, 84, 140);border-radius:8px;place-items:flex-start;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TVC广告分镜师</span></span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">，图中的产品是我这次TVC广告的主要展示产品，请你设计为这款产品设计一个展示食物极致美味的有点夸张的剧情故事，主人公是一个黑发亚洲男性，做成九宫格的分镜图，要求是黑白线稿风格，但要保持产品的一致</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(143, 149, 158) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">ps.因为目前sora2不支持上传真人图片，所以这里尽量都使用黑白线稿制作分镜图</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100019508\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5898148148148148\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/YEhakvKZjXk00diavJYADGFClnPAZrGPl6ibffzhiacMbGkO8I9kr5IeTlValUE0Z7Ix2mXLib9yFTUybMHmxQz2yw/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"341\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=478200a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FYEhakvKZjXk00diavJYADGFClnPAZrGPl6ibffzhiacMbGkO8I9kr5IeTlValUE0Z7Ix2mXLib9yFTUybMHmxQz2yw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&qu