面霜，产品的一致性非常强，原工作流是说英文，也可以通过修改提示语的方式让主播说中文，口播效果非常流畅。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用地址我贴这了 🔗 opencreator.io，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">说到这儿，我觉得得把幕后的人拎出来讲一下。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可能想不到，这样一个覆盖了三万多创作者、跑了十万多次生成的平台，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">一开始背后其实就三个人。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个导演，一个设计师，一个开发，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">三个人，就把这一整个工具给攒起来了，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">偏偏还挺好用。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">可能因为他们三个本质上都是创作者，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以 Open</span><span leaf=\"\">C</span><span leaf=\"\">reator 这套东西，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">骨子里就不是站在上帝视角教你怎么创作，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">而是尽量把创作过程中那些很烦、很碎、又不得不做的步骤，默默帮你搬掉。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单来说就是我只需要关注想要的内容是什么，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于中间流程只要一开始搭建一遍就够了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样我的脑子就都可以用来想玩法，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">而不是困在搭建的过程中，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">毕竟当年为ComfyUI熬过的夜，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我真的不想再来一遍了。</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">@ 作者 / 阿汤 &amp; 卡尔</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章展示了如何利用 AI 工具 OpenCreator 上的 Banana2 模型，通过简单的提示语和预设工作流，快速生成高质量 AI 商业广告视频，极大简化了视频制作流程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章展示了如何利用 AI 工具 OpenCreator 上的 Banana2 模型，通过简单的提示语和预设工作流，快速生成高质量 AI 商业广告视频，极大简化了视频制作流程。",
  "summary": "作者通过亲身体验，展示了使用 OpenCreator 平台及其 Banana2 模型，仅凭两段提示语和初始素材，即可生成多条具备高度一致性和专业度的 AI 商业广告视频，成功克服了早期 AI 生成视频在人物场景一致性、剧情完整度及转场运镜设计上的不足。文章详细介绍了该工作流的构建逻辑：首先利用 BananaPro 图生图功能生成九宫格分镜图，再通过 Sora2 或 Sora2pro 实现图生视频，自动完成剪辑、配音配乐。这种方法避免了手动剪辑和繁琐的后期制作，显著提升了视频成片率和制作效率。此外，文章还介绍了 OpenCreator 平台丰富的模型、组件及多样化的工作流模板，强调了其为创作者提供便捷、高效的 AI 视频生成解决方案，让创作者能够专注于内容创意而非技术实现。文章最后略微提到了 OpenCreator 是一个由三位创作者共同搭建的平台，这体现了“创作者为创作者服务”的理念，是其成功的关键之一。",
